{"tid":353815,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"畢咗業先發覺喺香港番工係有幾咁唔人道","createTime":"2017-08-10T02:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T03:41:59.000Z","uid":41790,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65b892e80f0f773079211f3166d58084cfb873e6","tid":353815,"uid":41790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:31:11.000Z","msg":"讀讀新聞系嗰陣，啲老師叫我地千其畢咗業唔好入大台tbb，人工低，自由度低。<br />\n<br />\n兩年後轉左讀新媒體，啲老師一樣叫我地畢咗業之後唔好入大台tbb。<br />\n<br />\n所以我嘅目光一直都冇放喺tbb身上，但係到到真正畢咗業搵工嗰陣發覺，如果想搵返同自己讀嗰科有關係嘅工，其實唔搵tbb真係好難搵野做。<br />\n<br />\n做大台之後嘅CV點都好睇啲，見左兩間電視台加幾間新媒體，只有tbb有second in嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n人工低，工作量高，工時長，做到隻狗咗都係得12k，無收工時間就常識，點解我仲會考慮佢？大台有系統，可以教我野，做完大台出到去會舒服啲。<br />\n<br />\n新媒體其實好多都係圍內幾個人圍威喂，有邊個平台啲片真係用心製作，有嘅都輪唔到請我啦，等入tbb做狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好，放完負，繼續做奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f24fe54bc8e8fc50af9c9d006d51eab36e47a08","tid":353815,"uid":41790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d03025844340cbc2c5697483509f49559906230","tid":353815,"uid":41790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49267a7782f939d270f2006e5fa4ca1dc50cbdc2","tid":353815,"uid":28870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:53:54.000Z","msg":"放完負就繼續做奴<br />\n咪撚推po取暖啦"},{"pid":"a82b4beb9e439936f9b3d7e0839576646c65bf04","tid":353815,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:55:39.000Z","msg":"由你選擇讀呢科已經知呢行係咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113e769e4988aad7610faa92045e5f9b4a45b13c","tid":353815,"uid":